        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer336588881" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13847048252286471707">I read this many years ago but confess I didn&apos;t &apos;get&apos; most of it. There were many inside jokes about historical figures of the age which I think I would understand a lot better now that I know the history of the period much better. As such I am anxious to reread. I remember at the time finding it very acerbic. </span>
  <span id="freeText13847048252286471707" style="display:none">I read this many years ago but confess I didn't 'get' most of it. There were many inside jokes about historical figures of the age which I think I would understand a lot better now that I know the history of the period much better. As such I am anxious to reread. I remember at the time finding it very acerbic. </span>
