        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2618109768" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4274424537083949356">An attack on man&apos;s fallen nature as universal as it is witty and nimble. Using the bedrock of man&apos;s sin and irrationality as his foundation, Erasmus builds a satirical edifice that casts a shadow on our hoi-polloi and intelligentsia just as it did on the peasants and popes of the 16th century.</span>
  <span id="freeText4274424537083949356" style="display:none">An attack on man's fallen nature as universal as it is witty and nimble. Using the bedrock of man's sin and irrationality as his foundation, Erasmus builds a satirical edifice that casts a shadow on our hoi-polloi and intelligentsia just as it did on the peasants and popes of the 16th century.</span>
